<h1>NS5 - Object Validation Made Simple</h1>

<h2>Getting Started</h2>

<p>Loads the library: e.g.</p>

```html
<script src="/path/to/ns5.min.js"></script>
```

<h2>Quick Example</h2>

<p>Say you want to make sure that this guy is 21 or older:</p>

```javascript
var this_guy = {
    name: 'john',
    age: 25
};
```

<p>Write an adult validator: e.g.</p>

```javascript
var is_adult = new NS5({
    age: function (value) {
        return value >= 21;
    }
});
```

<p>And then:</p>

```javascript
if ( is_adult.test(this_guy) ) {
    // do stuff...
}
```
